  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Mechanically ventilated

          -  ALI or ARDS

          -  No contraindications for prone position

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient &lt; 18 or &gt; 89 years old

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Elevated intracranial pressure

          -  PaO2/FiO2 - ratio &lt; 60

          -  ECMO

          -  Open abdomen

          -  Instable spine

          -  Malignant arrhythmias

          -  Severe hemodynamic instability
      </textblock>
